PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1778746039
OL,3,CWhat is behind the 'eerie' spring
OL,4,Cphenomenon covering Britain's
OL,5,Chedgerows?
OL,7,FWill we start seeing this more?
OL,9,FPossibly. Some scientists believe
OL,10,Fclimate patterns may be influencing
OL,11,Fhow frequently large-scale webbing
OL,12,Foccurs.
OL,14,FWarmer springs accelerate caterpillar
OL,15,Fdevelopment and improve winter
OL,16,Fsurvival, which potentially leads to
OL,17,Flarger colonies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
