OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1778746039
OL,3,CWhat is behind the 'eerie' spring
OL,4,Cphenomenon covering Britain's
OL,5,Chedgerows?
OL,7,FFor those willing to take a closer
OL,8,Flook, the webs reveal an intricate
OL,9,Fworld of caterpillars moving in
OL,10,Fsynchrony beneath thick blankets of
OL,11,Fsilk; transforming roadside shrubs
OL,12,Finto temporary monuments to nature's
OL,13,Fability to unsettle and fascinate in
OL,14,Fequal measure.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
